flowchart TD
    A([User runs: license-wizard]) --> LW[License Wizard]
    A -.->|flags| FL([Flags])
    FL -.-> LW
    LW -.->|reads config<br/>by store priority| LC[/Wizard config<br/>dot-file or manifest field/]
    LW -.->|reads license<br/>by manifest priority| PJ[/Project manifests/]

    LW --> HELP{--help flag?}

    %% ─── Help path ───
    HELP -->|Yes| HU[Print usage + flag listing]
    HU --> H

    HELP -->|No| NI{--license, --set, --get-tokens,<br/>or a --save-* flag given?}

    %% ─── Non-interactive CLI path ───
    NI -->|Yes| NIL{--license given?}
    NIL -->|No| ERRL[Error: --license required] --> H
    NIL -->|Yes| GT{--get-tokens flag?}
    GT -->|Yes| LT[List the copyright fields<br/>the license accepts] --> H
    GT -->|No| SV{--save-* location<br/>valid?}
    SV -->|more than one, or<br/>not present in project| ERRS[Report the save error] --> H
    SV -->|none, or exactly one valid| HS{--set values given?}
    HS -->|No| STD[Use official text unchanged]
    HS -->|Yes| RES[Resolve fields against<br/>the license's copyright slots]
    RES --> CHK{every required field<br/>supplied and recognized?}
    CHK -->|No| NEED[Report the missing or<br/>unknown copyright fields] --> H
    CHK -->|Yes| CUST[Render customized copyright]
    STD --> DR
    CUST --> DR

    %% ─── Dry-run gate (shared by both generation paths) ───
    DR{--dry-run flag given?}
    DR -->|Yes| DRP[Render the license to the terminal;<br/>skip every write — no LICENSE,<br/>config, or manifest update] --> H
    DR -->|No| PSV
    PSV[Persist config to the chosen save location,<br/>clearing the others — or, when skipped<br/>interactively, clearing every location]
    PSV -.->|writes or clears config| LC
    PSV --> G

    NI -->|No| M{--verify flag?}

    %% ─── Interactive / generation path ───
    M -->|No| C

    subgraph IO [Input Orchestrator]
        C[Prepare question]
        C --> D[Ask question]
        D --> E[Receive answer<br/>user accepts default or provides value]
        E --> INJ{answer injects<br/>follow-up questions?}
        INJ -->|license has customizable fields| MODE[Inject Standard / Customize choice]
        INJ -->|Customize selected| FIELDS[Inject one question per copyright field<br/>defaults pre-filled from saved tokens]
        INJ -->|none| F
        MODE --> F
        FIELDS --> F
        F{more questions?}
        F -->|Yes| C
        F -->|No| OG[Generate options object]
    end

    OG -->|options object| LW
    LW --> DR
    G[License is generated]
    G -->|writes license id<br/>to all present manifests| PJ
    G --> H([Done])

    %% ─── Verification path (standalone: ignores every other flag) ───
    M -->|Yes| V[Verify]
    V -.->|reads| EL[/Existing LICENSE file/]
    V -.->|re-renders license<br/>from saved config| LC
    V -.->|reads declared license<br/>of each present manifest| PJ
    V --> HASL{LICENSE file exists?}
    HASL -->|No| ERRNL[Error: no LICENSE to verify] --> H
    HASL -->|Yes| HASC{Saved config exists?}
    HASC -->|No| ERRNC[Error: no saved config] --> H
    HASC -->|Yes| R{LICENSE and every manifest's<br/>license in sync with config?<br/>file by hash, manifests by id}
    R -->|Yes| PASS([Pass])
    R -->|No| AG{--strict given?}
    AG -->|No, default| G2[Reconcile drift:<br/>rewrite LICENSE and/or<br/>update drifted manifests] --> H
    AG -->|Yes| FAIL([Fail: exit non-zero,<br/>report every drifted surface])
